Troubleshooting issues for workload running on Kubernetes, setting up logging and monitoring, and performance tuning.
 
Requirements:
Experience on AWS cloud services(VPC, EC2, IAM, CloudFront, API Gateway, Load Balancer, Elastic Kubernetes Service, Redshift, RDS, DynamoDB, Elasticache, Kafka, Lambda, Kinesis, Athena, S3 etc.., ).
Experience in container and container orchestration tools( Docker and Kubernetes) is must.
Experience in version control system and source code management (git, github and gitlab etc..,).
Experience in building & Manage the CICD pipeline through the DevOps model using Jenkins.
Experience in Linux and Windows operating systems.
Knowledge of networking and security.
Knowledge on databases.
